Package: glmADMM
Type: Package
Title: Solving Equality constrained L1-Regularized General Linear Models via ADMM
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-07-12
Author: Hui Jiang, Lan Luo
Maintainer: Lan Luo <luolsph@umich.edu>
Description: Fitting L1-regularization path for linear regression, logistic regression and Poisson regression. A major characteristic is that users can have an equality constraint on the coefficients. The algorithm uses Alternating Direction Method of Multipliers.
License: GPL-2

